    "raw_response": "Here is the analysis of the Nike brand:\n\nBRAND_PERSONALITY: Hero\n\nTARGET_AUDIENCE: Ambitious individuals who seek to push their limits and strive for excellence in various aspects of life.\n\nEMOTIONAL_APPEAL: Empowerment\n\nVISUAL_DIRECTION: Bold & kinetic, with a focus on high-contrast imagery that evokes energy and dynamism.\n\nMARKETING_TONE: Inspirational, yet authentic and relatable.\n\nCOLOR_STYLE: High-contrast dark, with bursts of vibrant colors to emphasize the brand's youthful and adventurous spirit.\n\nBRAND_NAME: Nike\n\nINDUSTRY: Sports & Fitness\n\nHEADLINE_1: Just Do It\n\nHEADLINE_2: Unleash Your Potential\n\nHEADLINE_3: Run Free. Live Free.\n\nTAGLINE_1: Find Your Greatness\n\nTAGLINE_2: Embrace Your Inner Athlete\n\nTAGLINE_3: For Every Moment, There's a Nike\n\nSOCIAL_POST: \"Take the leap and chase your dreams! #Nike #JustDoIt\"\n\nCTA_LINE: Just Do It\n\nMARKETING_PARAGRAPH: \"Don't let anyone or anything hold you back. Whether you're running, jumping, or just taking that first step, Nike is here to empower you to reach new heights. We believe in the power of human potential and strive to inspire greatness in everyone.\"\n\nKEY_FEATURE_1: Speed Focused\n\nKEY_FEATURE_2: Zero Lag\n\nKEY_FEATURE_3: High-Intensity Training\n\nPOSTER_PROMPT: \"Create an image that captures the essence of empowerment, with a bold, dynamic composition featuring a person in motion. Use a high-contrast color palette with bursts of vibrant colors to emphasize energy and dynamism. Typography should be clean and modern, with text overlaying the image in a way that creates visual interest.\"",
